{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21421.jpg","bgm":"bgm23_promised04","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102101,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"...What's going on?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Actually...in Promised Blood..."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"There are still some members targeting@the Magical Girls of Kamihama..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Eh...is that so?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102401,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Juri","textRight":"I thought we finally had things all settled..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102101,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"It can't be helped..."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Not everyone has sorted out their feelings."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"It'd be too convenient for everything@to be resolved all at once..."},{"chara":[{"id":102401,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Juri","textRight":"...Well, I guess that's true..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102101,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Me, you, Ao, Hikaru, and Ranka are all the same."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Right now, we've entered a new phase."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Everything is just beginning."},{"chara":[{"id":102101,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"That's why we're doing this interview...isn't it?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Yes, that's right..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102101,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"So, my apologies, but I have to go."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102401,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Juri","textRight":"We gotta persuade 'em..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"I-I understand!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Thank you very much for your time today!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102101,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"I would have liked to talk a little more, but..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"...Ah..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102401,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Juri","textRight":"What's wrong?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":102101,"lipSynch":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102101,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Juri, can you go ahead and meet up@with Ao and everyone else?"},{"chara":[{"id":102101,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"I'm going to check with Kagome and look over@what she wrote today, and then I'll be on my way."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102401,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Juri","textRight":"Huh? ...Geez, hurry up and get this done."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Yeah, I'll be right there in a second."},{"chara":[{"id":102401,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Juri","textRight":"Got it. Well then, see you later!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102401}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":102101,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":300,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Are you confirming what we talked about today?@Um..."},{"chara":[{"id":102101,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"That's not it."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Among us, there was definitely something that@changed."},{"chara":[{"id":102101,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"I just remembered it, so I wanted to request you@add one last thing."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"The change, you mean?"},{"chara":[{"id":102101,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Yes..."},{"bgm":"bgm03_story05","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Juri's magic is no longer running amok. "},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"No longer running amok...?@What does that mean...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102101,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"You see, Juri's stress is directly@linked to her magical power."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"As a result, it was a common occurrence@for her to have outbursts."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"But now, that's completely gone."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"...Could it be that..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102101,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Yes..."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"I think it may be because of those fourteen years..."},{"chara":[{"id":102101,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"I can't think of any other cause..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"I see..."},{"chara":[{"id":102101,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"The reason why I wanted to@tell you this at the end is... "},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Because I thought that this was a \"sign\"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"A \"sign\"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102101,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"A sign that we too can change..."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"I'm not sure if those fourteen years really did the@trick, but..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102101,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"I still wanted you to keep a record of it."},{"chara":[{"id":102101}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Just the fact that such a thing happened..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"...Yes, I understand."},{"chara":[{"id":102101,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Yuna","textLeft":"Thank you, and see you later."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102101}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":102001,"pos":1}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"(A sign of...change...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"...I guess I should head home too..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11_another/208101_aruchang.png","posX":0,"posY":-70,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bgm":"bgm20_song10","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"＜...＞"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<At this time, something was happening@with Kagome too...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Not just a sign, but a clear change...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Isn't that right? After all...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Kagome didn't use me to communicate even@once...>"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
